.TH DIV 3 ""
.UC 7
.SH NAME
div \- return quotient and remainder from division
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.ft B
#include <stdlib.h>

div_t
div(int num, int denom);
.ft R
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Div
computes the value
.I num/denom
and returns the quotient and remainder in a structure named
.B div_t
that contains two
.BR int
members named
.B quot
and
.BR rem .
.SH SEE ALSO
ldiv(3)
.SH STANDARDS
.B Div
conforms to ANSI X3.159-1989 (``ANSI C'').
